## OULAD Dataset License

This project uses the Open University Learning Analytics Dataset (OULAD), which is 
licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0).

Dataset Citation:
Kuzilek J., Hlosta M., Zdrahal Z. Open University Learning Analytics dataset 
Sci. Data 4:170171 doi: 10.1038/sdata.2017.171 (2017).

Dataset available at: https://analyse.kmi.open.ac.uk/open_dataset

When using this code with the OULAD dataset, please cite both this repository 
and the original OULAD dataset paper.